timeline.bodyText: Is this to suffix really the right way to go about this conflict? I would prefer to name it something like endermanTeleport, as (iirc) the function does other specific things to do with endermen, like play the teleport sound.
timeline.author: Earthcomputer

replies.bodyText: Named it teleportTo to match another method named teleportTo, which teleports to an entity instead of coordinates
replies.author: YanisBft
